 the orthogonality of eigenstates,\nand the unitarity of time evolution) are found not to be altered by the\nnoncommutativity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Jul 2011 15:10:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 7 Sep 2011 13:54:23 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 30 Nov 2011 08:18:56 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 19 Jun 2012 08:23:12 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Thu, 17 Apr 2014 09:37:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-06-06"}
