anced CNO cycle reaction rates to increase the\nmaximum luminosity of the first giant branch. However, it is impossible to\nreach the typical RGB tip luminosity even if all the reaction rates related to\nCNO cycles are enhanced by more than ten orders of magnitude.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Jul 2011 15:54:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-28"}
