74, KOI-81 and KIC10657664). This newly\ndiscovered binary offers the opportunity to study the evolution of a stripped\nred giant star through the pre-He-WD stage in great detail.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Jul 2011 15:57:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 29 Jul 2011 15:58:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-28"}
